                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Macon Geo</placeName>
                                        <date>March 19. 1849</date>.</p>
                              <p>Rev: Sir!</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I bespeak for my friend <persName>Doctor
                                                  Quintard</persName> a<lb/> favorable reception of
                                        his request. Knowing that you could<lb/> treat this subject
                                        better than any One I know, I have taken<lb/> the liberty to
                                        refer him to you.</p>
                              <p>I at the same time take this opportunity to request you<lb/> to
                                        send me a copy of the occident, beginning from last<lb/>
                                        <date><sic>Januar</sic></date>, and shall remit the amount
                                        of the yearly subscript,,<lb/>ion of $3. by receipt of the
                                        first number.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">I am, dear Sir</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">your very obedient Servant</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">
                                        <persName role="author">A. Dessan</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
